  },
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You target two creatures that are within 20 feet of each other within range and cause them to make a <strong>Strength saving throw</strong>  . If both targets fail, they are bound to one another by a spectral manacle.</p><p>For the duration, any damage done to either target is halved (rounded down) and then dealt to the other bound creature as well.</p><p>If the two bound creatures move more than 20 feet apart, the manacle breaks, dealing <strong>4d6 necrotic damage</strong> to each target.</p>",
